mattd implementation in plain C

This is exercise in writing a UNIX daemon. Heavily inspired by mattd <https://github.com/ralphbean/mattd>, but written from scratch with a little help from:

http://www.enderunix.org/docs/eng/daemon.php
http://www.netzmafia.de/skripten/unix/linux-daemon-howto.html
http://cjh.polyplex.org/software/daemon.pdf
